name: MekaVerse
description:
The MekaVerse is a collection of 8,888 generative Mekas inspired by the Japanese Anime universe. View the collection at https://themekaverse.com/gallery.

In the distant future, drivers fight in a world divided into 4 Factions. Originals Meka, Mirage, F9, and Gadians are the Titans who rule this planet. Which Faction are you going to join?

World map: https://worldmap.themekaverse.com/

Visit https://themekaverse.com/ for more details.
